<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.3.8">
<l>ericita ṟuñcarattā lilaṅkaiyiṉai taṉṉuṭaiya</l>
<l>varicilai vāyilpeytu vāykkōṭṭamta virttukanta</l>
<l>varaiyaṉama rummalaiya mararoṭukō ṉuñceṉṟu</l>
<l>tiricuṭar cūḻumalai tirumāliruñ cōlaiyatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain where abides the king who was satisfied</l>
<l rend="indent">having dispelled the complete crookedness of Laṅkā</l>
<l rend="indent">with fire spitting arrows rained down from the tip of his stripped bow,</l>
<l>the mountain where the king along with the celestials</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] the wandering sun and moon go to cirucumambulate</l>
<l>that is Tirumāliruñcōlai!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
